<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/404739-i-m-reading-the-painter-on-my-kindle-and">I&#39;m reading The Painter on my Kindle and have a question. Are there illustrations or images of his paintings in the hard copy book? There aren&#39;t any on the Kindle version.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_404739'><a id="like_count_community_question_404739" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/404739?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F18310201-the-painter">like</a></span>

