  <span id="freeText17910726685920915672" style="display:none">Whoa, Holy Shit Peter Heller. You have some crazy, profound, messed up shit in your head. And it makes for an amazing book!!! Deeply emotional, suspenseful at times, sentimental and heartwrenching, Peter Heller captures the calm of fishing as well as the action of being chased by a crazy truck driver, the beauty of art along with the ugliness of cold blooded murder. If you liked The Dog Stars you will love The Painter. If you haven't read The Dog Stars read them both. Peter Heller is a master, with a unique style and dark subject matter, he will thrill you, make you cry and make you cringe all on the same page.</span>
