<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer6098616823804559101"><i>There is more than one author in the Goodreads database with this name.</i><br/><br/><br/>Peter Heller holds an MFA from the Iowa Writers’ Workshop in both fiction and poetry. An award-winning adventure writer and longtime contributor to NPR, Heller is a contributing editor at Outside magazine, Men’s Journal, and National Geographic Adventure, and a regular contributor to Bloomberg Businessweek. He is also the autho</span>
  <span id="freeText6098616823804559101" style="display:none"><i>There is more than one author in the Goodreads database with this name.</i><br /><br /><br />Peter Heller holds an MFA from the Iowa Writers’ Workshop in both fiction and poetry. An award-winning adventure writer and longtime contributor to NPR, Heller is a contributing editor at Outside magazine, Men’s Journal, and National Geographic Adventure, and a regular contributor to Bloomberg Businessweek. He is also the author of several nonfiction books, including Kook, The Whale Warriors, and Hell or High Water: Surviving Tibet’s Tsangpo River. He lives in Denver, Colorado.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6098616823804559101" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
